Package com.ainq.fhir.utils

Class YamlParser

java.lang.Object
com.ainq.fhir.utils.YamlParser
All Implemented Interfaces:
ca.uhn.fhir.parser.IParser
public class YamlParser extends Object implements ca.uhn.fhir.parser.IParser
YamlParser implements the HAPI FHIR IParser interface, enabling it to be used to convert FHIR Resources and elements to and from YAML
Author:
Audacious Inquiry
